<title>Countries index | Sancbook</title>


<h1>Countries index</h1>
<p>Currently <%= @countries.size %> countries on the list.</p>
<p>If your favourite country is not on the list, why not start sancitoning people* from that country now?</p>
<br>
<div class="country_index">
    <% @countries.each do |country| %>
        <div class='thumb'>
            <a href="/countries/<%= country["id"] %>">
                <img src="<%= country.flag %>" alt="<%= country["name"] %>">
                <figcaption><%= country["name"] %></figcaption>
            </a>
        
        </div>
    <% end%>
</div>
<br><br><br>
<p style="font-size:small;inline-height:50%">*who have commited serious violations or serious abuses of human rights</p>